bower search  <library name>                    -> search for library to download it

i.e(bower search bootstrap)

bower install <library name>                    ->to install library it also install dependencies

i.e (bower install bootstrap)  it also install jquery as dependence for it 


bower init       -> to make json file to put dependences and other thing to distribute them for other developers


uninstall <library name>               -> to uninstall library if i download it and you made a mistake and you want to install different library





